                If you want to self-manage, the <a href="https://meridiangable.com" data-affiliate data-vendor="meridiangable">Thinkrr AI platform</a> starts at $83/month with everything you need. If you want it done for you with HVAC-specific configuration, <a href="https://meridiangable.com" data-affiliate data-vendor="meridiangable">Meridian Gable</a> handles the full setup and management.
              </p>

              <div style="background: #f0f7ff; border-left: 4px solid #1B4F72; padding: 20px 24px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;">
                <p style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 8px 0; color: #1B4F72;">Try it right now</p>
